  <brief_title>A Portion-controlled Diet Will Prevent Weight Gain in Diabetics Treated With ACTOS</brief_title>
  <acronym>TAKE II</acronym>
  <official_title>A Portion-controlled Diet Will Prevent Weight Gain in Diabetics Treated With ACTOS</official_title>
